{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8ce43f0f-a8e4-433f-a331-f4e5a5c0b74d",
    "name": "Task Service",
    "description": "Ручное тестирование REST API Task Service.\n\n**Базовый URL (dev через nginx):** `{{baseUrl}}`\n**Прямой доступ к API (без nginx):** `{{baseUrlDirect}}`\n**WebSocket:** см. папку **Realtime (WebSocket)** — подключение только через **New → WebSocket**, не через HTTP-запросы.\n\n**Порядок smoke-проверки:**\n1. System → Health\n2. Auth → Login (save token)\n3. Projects → Create Project\n4. Tasks → Create Task → … → Reopen Task (сначала перевести в `done`)\n\nDev-пользователи после `migrate`: `admin@example.dev` / `user@example.dev`, пароль `password123`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Realtime Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health/realtime"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (save token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', data.access_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/token"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
